{"tid":1718661,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"[文宣組請入] 道路研究社推出「路面字體」","createTime":"2019-11-14T01:54:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T01:55:42.000Z","uid":36073,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b2d41733d96d039c9c9436bfaf52d99db67dd259","tid":1718661,"uid":36073,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T01:54:37.000Z","msg":"【香港路面文字（得英文）】<br />\n今日我地推出第一套字體（不過唔係監獄體🙈），係仿製路面文字。雖然呢隻字體無咩用，得英文大楷，又無中文。不過歡迎你用嚟做文宣都好，印出黎做 stencil 又可以；希望可以藉此鼓勵香港人。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/p960x960/75362201_3417334471624947_6357398471141490688_o.jpg?_nc_cat=106&amp;_nc_oc=AQkNtvPTc_4OAttYzqJkftl8JuzAjQwkOWNTox_mRW-agKoe_JI1EiwP2CAR4M4N674&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-hkg3-1.xx&amp;oh=d2d7be28e8d056dc5c2b27ab4994c5fc&amp;oe=5E8CE06C\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent-hkg3-1.xx.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Fp960x960%2F75362201_3417334471624947_6357398471141490688_o.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D106%26_nc_oc%3DAQkNtvPTc_4OAttYzqJkftl8JuzAjQwkOWNTox_mRW-agKoe_JI1EiwP2CAR4M4N674%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent-hkg3-1.xx%26oh%3Dd2d7be28e8d056dc5c2b27ab4994c5fc%26oe%3D5E8CE06C&h=17dc7cf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>（非商用卽可）</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n下載：<br />\n<a href=\"https://drive.google.com/file/d/1PR93LBWftvmWUvbFIFmFLMayVNP-mYRv/view?fbclid=IwAR1Bk3iW_Tx-a0mr-V4KgeAp_QI7szxV75tp_xH44AoGDQK22fqaoDutV80\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fdrive.google.com%2Ffile%2Fd%2F1PR93LBWftvmWUvbFIFmFLMayVNP-mYRv%2Fview%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR1Bk3iW_Tx-a0mr-V4KgeAp_QI7szxV75tp_xH44AoGDQK22fqaoDutV80&d=Ue9aQsdn%2FMYV7LryoIv%2BZLM5QgR%2FpIHXQ%2BfAgFWVWJ0%3D&h=f9e5f3dc\" target=\"_blank\">https://drive.google.com/file/d/1PR93LBWftvmWUvbFIFmFLMayVNP-mYRv/view?fbclid=IwAR1Bk3iW_Tx-a0mr-V4KgeAp_QI7szxV75tp_xH44AoGDQK22fqaoDutV80</a><br />\n<br />\n入去 Like 或 Share 個post 都好<br />\nRoad Research Society 道路硏究社<br />\n<a href=\"htt